  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/05254ddb07bc578525f2b12cc22c7df2.poster.avif?t=1743654804\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/05254ddb07bc578525f2b12cc22c7df2.webm?t=1743654804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/05254ddb07bc578525f2b12cc22c7df2.mp4?t=1743654804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the king's throne and immerse yourself in a world full of tough choices and unexpected challenges. Your kingdom is in danger, and its future depends solely on you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speak with heroes, making life-changing decisions. Every \"yes\" or \"no\" affects your resources. Achieve your goal within a limited time and discover the consequences of your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/99224d8f913fd101d18f2a2751fb1843.poster.avif?t=1743654804\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/99224d8f913fd101d18f2a2751fb1843.webm?t=1743654804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/99224d8f913fd101d18f2a2751fb1843.mp4?t=1743654804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your resources wisely, gather allies, and plan your actions to strengthen your kingdom. Enjoy continuing to develop your state.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you become the ruler who will be remembered for centuries?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/ee216f4b792dbe76fbdbcddba4d7891e.poster.avif?t=1743654804\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/ee216f4b792dbe76fbdbcddba4d7891e.webm?t=1743654804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/ee216f4b792dbe76fbdbcddba4d7891e.mp4?t=1743654804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >make difficult decisions</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >develop your city</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >manage resources skillfully</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >meet many unusual characters with their own needs</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras/8c99b97f0f9d6964d00c1a3c91de74c5.avif?t=1743654804\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457740/extras_big/8c99b97f0f9d6964d00c1a3c91de74c5.avif?t=1743654804 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
